\date{2024-07-22}
\title{Extensive category}
\taxon{definition}
\meta{external}{https://ncatlab.org/nlab/show/extensive+category}
\p{A [category](math-000D) with [coproducts](math-004D) is \em{extensive} if}

\ul{
  \li{[pullbacks](math-000J) along coproduct injections exist}
  \li{finite coproducts are [disjoint](math-004E)}
  \li{finite coproducts are [stable under pullback](math-004F)}
}